{"title_page": "Segundo Sol", "text_new": "{{short description|Brazilian telenovela by Jo\u00e3o Emanuel Carneiro}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2019}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name                = Segundo Sol\n| image                    = Segundo_Sol_logo.png\n| image_upright            = \n| image_size               = 255px\n| image_alt                = \n| caption                  = \n| show_name_2              = A Second Chance\n| genre                    = [[Telenovela]]\n| creator                  = [[Jo\u00e3o Emanuel Carneiro]]\n| writer                   = \n| screenplay               = \n| story                    = \n| director                 = {{Plainlist|\n* Dennis Carvalho\n* Maria de M\u00e9dicis\n}}\n| creative_director        = \n| starring                 = {{plainlist|\n* [[Giovanna Antonelli]]\n* Em\u00edlio Dantas\n* [[Deborah Secco]]\n* [[Adriana Esteves]]\n* [[Vladimir Brichta]]\n* Fabr\u00edcio Boliveira\n* [[Chay Suede]]\n* [[Nanda Costa]]\n* [[Let\u00edcia Colin]]\n* [[Fabiula Nascimento]]\n* [[Maria Luiza Mendon\u00e7a]]\n* [[Luisa Arraes]]\n* [[Caco Ciocler]]\n* Danilo Mesquita\n* [[Jos\u00e9 de Abreu]]\n* [[Arlete Salles]]\n}}\n| narrated                 = \n| theme_music_composer     = \n| opentheme                = \"O Segundo Sol\" by BaianaSystem\n| endtheme                 = \n| composer                 = \n| country                  = Brazil\n| language                 = Portuguese\n| num_seasons              = \n| num_episodes             = 155 (135 international version)<ref>https://screening.globo.com/content/a-second-chance</ref>\n| list_episodes            = \n| executive_producer       = \n| producer                 = \n| location                 = [[Salvador, Bahia]]\n| cinematography           = \n| editor                   = \n| camera                   = [[Multi-camera]]\n| runtime                  = 30\u201367 minutes\n| company                  = [[Est\u00fadios Globo]]\n| distributor              = \n| budget                   = \n| network                  = [[Rede Globo]]\n| picture_format           = [[HDTV]] [[1080i]]\n| audio_format             = \n| first_aired              = {{Start date|2018|5|14|df=y}}\n| last_aired               = {{End date|2018|11|9|df=y}}\n| preceded_by              = ''[[O Outro Lado do Para\u00edso]]''\n| followed_by              = ''[[O S\u00e9timo Guardi\u00e3o]]''\n| website                  = https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol\n| production_website       = \n}}\n\n'''''Segundo Sol''''' (English: '''''A Second Chance'''''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/global/natpe-brazil-avenues-joao-emanuel-carneiro-second-chance-1203113715/|title=NATPE: \u2018Brazil Avenue\u2019s\u2019 Joao Emanuel Carneiro on \u2018A Second Chance\u2019|date=|first=|last=|accessdate=|website=Variety|language=English}}</ref>) is a Brazilian [[telenovela]] produced and broadcast by [[Rede Globo]] that premiered on 14 May 2018, replacing ''[[O Outro Lado do Para\u00edso]]'', and ended on 9 November 2018, with a total of 155 episodes. It is created by [[Jo\u00e3o Emanuel Carneiro]] and directed by Dennis Carvalho.\n\nSet in both 1999 and present time, in Bahia, ''Segundo Sol'' gives a trajectory of singer, Beto Falc\u00e3o, who is forced to fake his death in order to save his family from financial turmoil. In his new identity, named Miguel, he meets Luzia, fishmonger and a mother of two, and an estranged wife to a dead beat; they become romantically involved. Karola, Beto's ex-girlfriend and Laureta Bottini, a brothel-keeper, frame Luzia in the murder of her husband and she is forced to flee, leaving her children behind. Nearly two decades later, Luzia returns as Ariella, a DJ and tries to rebuild her life by reuniting with her children, clearing her name, and  rekindle her love story with Beto / Miguel.\n\nThe show stars [[Giovanna Antonelli]], [[Adriana Esteves]], Em\u00edlio Dantas, [[Deborah Secco]], [[Vladimir Brichta]], together with a large ensemble cast.\n\n==Plot==\nSet in [[Salvador, Bahia|Salvador]] in 1999, in the historic district of Santo Antonio, lives the Falc\u00e3o family. Beto, one of the four sons of Dod\u00f4 and Nana, made his fame as a singer of [[Ax\u00e9 (music)|ax\u00e9]], but for about three years he has experienced the bitter taste of ostracism. The family earns their livelihood from the crab bar in the same house where they live, but runs the risk of losing their home because of the mismanagement of Beto's career by his manager and brother Remy, the \"black sheep\" son. To help pay part of the debt, Beto agrees to perform in [[Aracaju]], when the plane he had planned to take crashes at sea and he is presumed dead. Due to the unexpected nationwide commotion, the singer is convinced by Remy and his girlfriend Karola \u2014 with whom his relationship is very shaken \u2014 to continue passing off as a deceased man by staying in the fictional island of Boipor\u00e3. It is at this moment the troubled Beto meets Luzia ([[Giovanna Antonelli]]), a fishwife, abandoned by her husband, fending alone for her young children. The two fall in love and soon make plans for marriage, without her knowing the true identity of Beto, who presents himself as Miguel. Hostage of a large plot orchestrated by Karola and Laureta ([[Adriana Esteves]]), the couple ends up separated. They find her ex-husband and he tries to kill Beto but Luzia ends up killing him. Luzia, now a fugitive, flees to [[Iceland]], with the help of Goa (Andr\u00e9 Dias) where she becomes famous as DJ Ariela.\n\n===Second phase===\nAfter nearly 20 years, Luzia returns to try to reunite her shattered family, without imagining that Miguel, her great love that she could not forget, is the famous singer Beto Falc\u00e3o. Along with his family, Beto maintains to this day the farce of his death and is unhappy with the course that life has taken. He also keeps his love for Luzia alive and goes crazy when he discovers that the fishmonger, now a successful DJ, is in Salvador and will do everything to find her and rekindle their past romances.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://telepadi.folha.uol.com.br/carminha-missao-adriana-esteves-reencontra-joao-emanuel-carneiro/|title=Carminha, a miss\u00e3o: Adriana Esteves reencontra Jo\u00e3o Emanuel Carneiro |date=|first=|last=|accessdate=|website=Telepadi|language=Portuguese}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n{{div col}}\n* [[Giovanna Antonelli]] as Luzia Batista / Ariella<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/giovanna-antonelli-sera-luzia-em-segundo-sol-proxima-novela-das-9.ghtml|title=Giovanna Antonelli ser\u00e1 Luzia em 'Segundo Sol', pr\u00f3xima novela das 9|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|date=29 March 2018|title=Giovanna Antonelli muda o visual e mostra loiro com fios platinados para 'Segundo Sol' \u2013 Gshow|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/giovanna-antonelli-muda-o-visual-e-mostra-loiro-com-fios-platinados-para-segundo-sol.ghtml|journal=Gshow|language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/giovanna-antonelli-mudara-o-visual-para-segundo-sol.ghtml|title=Giovanna Antonelli muda o visual, e p\u00fablico faz aposta; confira!|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* [[:pt:Emilio Dantas|Emilio Dantas]] as Roberto \"Beto\" Falc\u00e3o / Miguel<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/emilio-dantas-exibe-dreads-para-fase-inicial-de-beto-falcao-seu-personagem-em-segundo-sol.ghtml|title=Emilio Dantas exibe dreads para fase inicial de Beto Falc\u00e3o, seu personagem em 'Segundo Sol'|date=3 April 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/emilio-dantas-grava-segundo-sol-na-bahia-e-tira-foto-com-fa.ghtml|title=Emilio Dantas grava 'Segundo Sol' na Bahia e tira foto com f\u00e3|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/emilio-dantas-e-giovanna-antonelli-farao-casal-em-segundo-sol.ghtml|title=Emilio Dantas e Giovanna Antonelli far\u00e3o casal em 'Segundo Sol'|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* [[Deborah Secco]] as Caroline \"Karola\" Falc\u00e3o<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/deborah-secco-sera-a-vila-karola-em-segundo-sol-veja-a-1-foto.ghtml|title=Deborah Secco ser\u00e1 a vil\u00e3 Karola em 'Segundo Sol': veja a 1\u00aa foto|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/deborah-secco-grava-cenas-de-segundo-sol-na-bahia.ghtml|title=Deborah Secco grava cenas de 'Segundo Sol' na Bahia|date=20 March 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref name=\"Karola & Laureta\">{{cite web|url=https://observatoriodatelevisao.bol.uol.com.br/entrevista/2018/04/formando-uma-dupla-de-vilas-com-adriana-esteves-em-segundo-sol-deborah-secco-declara-nao-posso-decepcionar-meu-idolo|title=Formando uma dupla de vil\u00e3s com Adriana Esteves em Segundo Sol, Deborah Secco declara: \"N\u00e3o posso decepcionar meu \u00eddolo\"|publisher=Observat\u00f3rio de Televis\u00e3o|accessdate=11 May 2018|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* [[Adriana Esteves]] as Laureta Botini / Divin\u00e9ia dos Santos<ref name=\"Karola & Laureta\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/adriana-esteves-muda-visual-para-segundo-sol.ghtml|title=Adriana Esteves muda visual para \u2018Segundo Sol\u2019|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://observatoriodatelevisao.bol.uol.com.br/capitulo-da-novela/segundo-sol/2018/04/conheca-laureta-uma-das-malvadas-de-segundo-sol-proxima-novela-das-21h|title=Conhe\u00e7a Laureta, uma das malvadas de Segundo Sol, pr\u00f3xima novela das 21h|publisher=Observat\u00f3rio de Televis\u00e3o|date=25 April 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|author=Jo\u00e3o Paulo Reis|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* [[Vladimir Brichta]] as Remildo \"Remy\" Falc\u00e3o<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/vladimir-brichta-sera-remy-em-segundo-sol-veja-1-foto.ghtml|title=Vladimir Brichta ser\u00e1 Remy em 'Segundo Sol'; veja 1\u00aa foto!|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* [[Jos\u00e9 de Abreu]] as Dorival \"Dod\u00f4\" Falc\u00e3o<ref name=\"Dod\u00f4 & Nan\u00e1\">{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/jose-de-abreu-e-arlete-salles-farao-casal-em-segundo-sol.ghtml|title=Jos\u00e9 de Abreu e Arlete Salles far\u00e3o casal em 'Segundo Sol'|date=21 March 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* [[Arlete Salles]] as Nazira \"Nan\u00e1\" Falc\u00e3o<ref name=\"Dod\u00f4 & Nan\u00e1\" />\n* Fabr\u00edcio Boliveira as Roberval Santos<ref>{{cite web|url=https://observatoriodatelevisao.bol.uol.com.br/entrevista/2018/04/ele-e-filho-de-uma-traicao-da-mae-com-o-patrao-revela-fabricio-boliveira-sobre-roberval-personagem-de-segundo-sol|title=\"Ele \u00e9 filho de uma trai\u00e7\u00e3o da m\u00e3e com o patr\u00e3o\", revela Fabr\u00edcio Boliveira sobre Roberval, personagem de Segundo Sol|publisher=Observat\u00f3rio de Televis\u00e3o|accessdate=11 May 2018|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* [[Caco Ciocler]] as Edgar Athayde<ref>{{cite web|url=https://extra.globo.com/tv-e-lazer/telinha/caco-ciocler-sera-homem-culto-sem-talento-para-os-negocios-em-segundo-sol-22567060.html|title=Caco Ciocler ser\u00e1 homem culto e sem talento para os neg\u00f3cios em 'Segundo sol'|date=9 April 2018|accessdate=11 May 20