\u00e3s em 'Segundo Sol', pr\u00f3xima novela das 9|date=7 March 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* [[:pt:Giovanna Lancelloti|Giovanna Lancelloti]] as Rochelle Athayde\n* [[:pt:Armando Babaioff|Armando Babaioff]] as Ionan Falc\u00e3o<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/armando-babaioff-sera-ionan-em-segundo-sol-proxima-novela-das-9.ghtml|title=Armando Babaioff ser\u00e1 Ionan em 'Segundo Sol', pr\u00f3xima novela das 9|date=14 March 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/Famosos/noticia/armando-babaioff-celebra-boa-fase-profissional-com-trabalhos-no-teatro-e-na-tv-sou-um-artista-sou-inquieto.ghtml|title=Armando Babaioff celebra boa fase profissional com trabalhos no teatro e na TV: 'Sou um artista, sou inquieto'|date=19 March 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* [[Roberta Rodrigues]] as Doralice\n* Danilo Ferreira as Ac\u00e1cio Pereira\n* Luis Lobianco as Cl\u00f3vis Falc\u00e3o<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/luis-lobianco-estreia-na-proxima-novela-das-9-segundo-sol.ghtml|title=Luis Lobianco estreia na pr\u00f3xima novela das 9, 'Segundo Sol'|date=12 March 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/Famosos/noticia/luis-lobianco-encara-projeto-desafiador-no-teatro-e-celebra-primeira-novela-era-o-momento-de-viver-isso.ghtml|title=Luis Lobianco encara projeto desafiador no teatro e celebra primeira novela: 'Era o momento de viver isso'|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* Thalita Carauta as Gorete\n* Andr\u00e9 Dias as Groa<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/andre-dias-sera-parceiro-de-giovanna-antonelli-em-segundo-sol-veja-antes-e-depois.ghtml|title=Andr\u00e9 Dias ser\u00e1 parceiro de Giovanna Antonelli em 'Segundo Sol'; veja antes e depois|date=19 March 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* Claudia di Moura as Josefa \"Zefa\" Santos\n* Jo\u00e3o Acaiabe as Pai Didico<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gshow.globo.com/novelas/segundo-sol/noticia/segundo-sol-coletiva-reune-elenco-direcao-e-joao-emanuel-carneiro.ghtml|title='Segundo Sol': coletiva re\u00fane elenco nos Est\u00fadios Globo|date=26 April 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Gshow|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* Roberto Bonfim as Agenor C\u00e2mara \n* Kelzy Ecard as Eunice \"Nice\" C\u00e2mara\n* Gabriela Moreyra as Renata \"Renatinha\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://oplanetatv.clickgratis.com.br/noticias/bastidores/gabriela-moreyra-faz-sua-estreia-na-globo-em-segundo-sol.html|title=Gabriela Moreyra faz sua estreia na Globo em Segundo Sol|date=17 April 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=OplanetaTV|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* [[Antonio Pitanga]] as Pai de Santo<ref>{{cite web|url=https://oplanetatv.clickgratis.com.br/noticias/bastidores/antonio-pitanga-vivera-pai-de-santo-em-segundo-sol.html|title=Ant\u00f4nio Pitanga viver\u00e1 pai de santo em Segundo Sol|date=26 February 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=OplanetaTV|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* Osmar Silveira as Narciso Rangel\n* Pablo Morais as Tom\u00e9<ref>{{cite web|url=https://oplanetatv.clickgratis.com.br/noticias/bastidores/autor-convida-pablo-morais-para-proxima-novela-das-9.html|title=Autor convida Pablo Morais para pr\u00f3xima novela das 9|date=6 March 2018|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=OplanetaTV|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* Robertha Portella as Ariadna<ref>{{cite web|url=https://oplanetatv.clickgratis.com.br/noticias/bastidores/robertha-portella-faz-sua-estreia-na-dramaturgia-da-globo.html|title=Robertha Portella faz sua estreia na dramaturgia da Globo|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=OplanetaTV|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* Hugo Moura as Robinson \"Robinho\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://extra.globo.com/tv-e-lazer/telinha/marido-de-deborah-secco-hugo-moura-fara-garoto-de-programa-em-segundo-sol-22610037.html|title=Marido de Deborah Secco, Hugo Moura far\u00e1 garoto de programa em 'Segundo sol'|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Extra|author=Carla Bittencourt|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* Fernando Sampaio<ref>{{cite web|url=http://noticiasdetv.com/2018/03/09/conheca-a-historia-e-o-elenco-completo-da-novela-segundo-sol/|title=Conhe\u00e7a a hist\u00f3ria e o elenco completo da novela \"Segundo Sol\"|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Not\u00edcias de TV|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* Marcelo Augusto\n* Paulo Borges as Edilei\n* Carol Fazu as Selma\n* Drayson Menezes as Wander<ref>{{cite web|url=https://extra.globo.com/tv-e-lazer/telinha/drayson-menezes-irmao-de-sheron-menezzes-vai-fazer-segundo-sol-22646235.html|title=Drayson Menezes, irm\u00e3o de Sheron Menezzes, vai fazer 'Segundo sol'|accessdate=11 May 2018|publisher=Extra|author=Reda\u00e7\u00e3o|language=pt-BR}}</ref>\n* Narcival Rubens as Galdino Navarro\n* Zeca de Abreu as Janu\u00e1ria\n* Ciro Sales as Du Love\n* \u00cdcaro Zulu as Dorival \"Doni\" Falc\u00e3o Neto\n* Vinicius Nascimento\n* Ygor Rodrigues as Tup\u00e3\n* Ittalo Paix\u00e3o\n* Bia Barros\n* Larissa Marques\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Guest cast===\n* [[Chico Diaz]] as Miguel Batista\n* Thales Miranda as young \u00cdcaro\n* Rafaela Brazil as young Manuela\n\n==Production==\n[[Jo\u00e3o Emanuel Carneiro]] began developing the series in October 2016.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://observatoriodatelevisao.bol.uol.com.br/noticia-da-tv/2016/10/autor-de-avenida-brasil-joao-emanuel-carneiro-escreve-nova-novela-na-globo|title=Autor de Avenida Brasil, Jo\u00e3o Emanuel Carneiro escreve nova novela na Globo|date=|first=|last=|accessdate=26 May 2018|website=O Globo|language=Portuguese}}</ref> Initially the show was tentatively under the title ''Da Volta Pra Casa'', but was later changed to ''Segundo Sol''.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://kogut.oglobo.globo.com/noticias-da-tv/noticia/2017/12/segundo-sol-sera-o-titulo-da-novela-de-joao-emanuel-carneiro-dirigida-por-dennis-carvalho.html|title='Segundo sol' ser\u00e1 o t\u00edtulo da novela de Jo\u00e3o Emanuel Carneiro|date=|first=|last=|accessdate=26 May 2018|website=O Globo|language=Portuguese}}</ref> In January 2017 the synopsis was presented to the network and was approved, giving endorsement for the creator to continue developing the story and enter into phase of pre-production for the 2018\u201319 season.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://kogut.oglobo.globo.com/noticias-da-tv/coluna/noticia/2017/01/joao-emanuel-carneiro-trabalha-na-sinopse-de-sua-nova-novela-que-estreara-em-outubro-de-2018.html|title=Jo\u00e3o Emanuel Carneiro trabalha na sinopse de sua nova novela|date=|first=|last=|accessdate=26 May 2018|work=[[O Globo]]|language=Portuguese}}</ref>  The approval of a telenovela in [[Bahia]] was a strategic move, since it was a state where [[Rede Globo]] did not reach the top spot for years, second to [[RecordTV]]'s productions.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://noticiasdatv.uol.com.br/noticia/televisao/na-terra-da-nova-novela-das-nove-da-globo-ate-jornal-nacional-perde-para-record-20330|title=Na terra da nova novela das nove da Globo, at\u00e9 o Jornal Nacional perde para a Record|date=|first=|last=|accessdate=26 May 2018|publisher=O Planeta TV|language=Portuguese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/may/18/brazil-segundo-sol-telenovela-white-black-cast-race|title=Bahia is Brazil's blackest state \u2013 but you'd never guess it from latest TV soap|last=Cowie|first=Sam|work=[[The Guardian]]|publisher=Guardian Media Group|date=18 May 2018|accessdate=30 June 2018}}</ref>\n\n===Filming===\nIn October 2017, the set design team was sent to [[Bahia]] in search for small villages with preserved natural beauty to be the backdrop of the first phase.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://oplanetatv.clickgratis.com.br/noticias/bastidores/de-volta-pra-casa-equipe-vai-a-bahia-escolher-locacoes.html|title=De Volta Pra Casa: Equipe vai \u00e0 Bahia escolher loca\u00e7\u00f5es|date=|first=|last=|accessdate=26 May 2018|publisher=O Planeta TV|language=Portuguese}}</ref> Despite the synopsis of the first phase set in Boipeba in [[Cairu]], the production crew decided not use it due lack of infrastructure to carry the equipments, choosing to record the scenes in another city\u2014Cara\u00edva\u2014but the team faced difficulties; the Municipal Environmental Council of Cara\u00edva was against the recordings, fearing that exposing the place at national level could attract an exaggerated tourism and generate degradation of the natural ecosystem.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sulbahianews.com.br/moradores-de-caraiva-rejeitam-gravacoes-de-novela-da-globo/|title=Moradores de Cara\u00edva rejeitam grava\u00e7\u00f5es de novela da Globo|date=|first=|last=|accessdate=26 May 2018|publisher=Sul Bahia News|language=Portuguese}}</ref> In order to decide the impasse, the Council established a referendum, in which 88% of the village population voted against filming the show there.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://natelinha.uol.com.br/novelas/2017/11/24/moradores-de-comunidade-rejeitam-gravacoes-de-novela-da-globo-na-bahia-112362.php|title=Moradores de comunidade rejeitam grava\u00e7\u00f5es de novela da Globo na Bahia|date=|first=|last=|accessdate=26 May 2018|publisher=Natelinha TV|language=Portuguese}}</ref>\n\nOn 7 December 2017, it was announced that the recordings would take place in [[Trancoso, Bahia|Trancoso]], a village in [[Porto Seguro]], which had already benefited from the tourism brought by the recording of the DVD, ''Ac\u00fastico em Trancoso'' by [[Ivete Sangalo]] in 2016.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://oplanetatv.clickgratis.com.br/noticias/bastidores/de-volta-pra-casa-sera-gravada-em-trancoso-na-bahia.html|title=De Volta Pra Casa ser\u00e1 gravada em Trancoso, na Bahia|date=|first=|last=|accessdate=26 May 2018|publisher=Oplaneta TV TV|language=Portuguese}}</ref> The two houses used by the protagonists were not scenographic; they were actually built on the beach specifically for recordings and donated to local residents after filming ended.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://observatoriodatelevisao.bol.uol.com.br/noticia-da-tv/2017/12/globo-constroi-casas-na-bahia-para-gravacao-de-nova-trama-das-21h|title=Globo constr\u00f3i casas na Bahia para grava\u00e7\u00e3o de nova trama das 21h|date=|first=|last=|accessdate=26 May 2018|website=Noticias da TV TV|language=Portuguese}}</ref> In February 2018, Emilio Dantas, [[Deborah Secco]] and [[Adriana Esteves]] travelled to [[Salvador, Bahia|Salvador]] and recorded the first scenes of the telenovela during the 2018 Carnival. In March, besides the fore mentioned three, [[Giovanna Antonelli]], [[Vladimir Brichta]], [[Arlete Salles]], [[Jos\u00e9 de Abreu]], [[Fabiula Nascimento]], Armando Babaioff and Luis Lobianco also began filming the first phase in Salvador and Trancoso.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://oplanetatv.clickgratis.com.br/noticias/bastidores/elenco-de-segundo-sol-viaja-para-gravar-em-trocoso-bahia.html#ixzz5GFpDYjnW|title=Elenco de Segundo Sol viaja para gravar em Trancoso, Bahia|date=|first=Patr\u00edcia|last=Kogut|accessdate=26 May 2018|website=O Planeta TV|language=Portuguese}}</ref> The city was built in the scenic [[Est\u00fadios Globo]], compiling the houses of the characters, as well as replica of the district of San Antonio.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aloalobahia.com/fotos/globo-reproduz-bairro-de-salvador-em-cidade-cenografica-de-segundo-sol|title=Globo reproduz bairro de Salvador em cidade cenogr\u00e1fica de \"Segundo Sol\"|date=|first=|last=|accessdate=26 May 2018|website=Al\u00f4 Bahia|language=Portuguese}}</ref>\n\n==Soundtrack=